Please be aware that there is no way to recover your funds if you lose your wallet keys. Without your PUBLIC WALLET, PRIVATE SPEND and PRIVATE VIEW keys you cannot ever recover your Electroneum you send to this wallet so keep the PDF or paper print out VERY SAFE.

Electroneum paper (offline) wallet generator

Important information
  1. Each wallet created is unique, you can not access a previous created wallet via this tool, keep the generated pdf safe!
  2. If you lose your public wallet address, private spend or private view keys you lose access to the wallet, keep the generated pdf safe!

For maximum security you should download a version to run from a USB stick on a PC or MAC that is not connected to the Internet. (Download a zip here). If you are more trusting, you should still think about running this page in an incognito window (or private window) with your browser extensions switched off.

Move your mouse

Wiggle your mouse around this area to start generating your Electroneum wallet!
Randomness Progress:

You're Electroneum wallet is ready

To safeguard this wallet it is important to print (or save) the pdf and store it in a safe location.

Remember to keep your printed wallet in a zip lock bag to keep it safe from water.

Treat this paper wallet like cash

If you leave/refresh the site or press the "Generate New Address" button then a new wallet will be generated and the previously wallet will not be retrievable.

Your Electroneum PRIVATE SPEND key should be kept a secret. Whomever you share the PRIVATE SPEND key with has access to spend all the Electroneum coins associated with that address.

This site DOES NOT have knowledge of your PRIVATE SPEND key, but you should ideally run this page in a private (incognito) tab with browser extensions turned off.
